                        <h3><a href="#">Funding Source(s)</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>All external funding for measure development has been received and used in full compliance with The Joint Commission's Corporate Sponsorship policies, which are available upon written request to The Joint Commission.</p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Composition of the Group that Developed the Measure</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Technical advisory panel of stakeholders. Panel membership may be viewed at: <a href="/web/20180625152856/https://www.qualitymeasures.ahrq.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=49182&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3a%2f%2fwww.jointcommission.org%2fassets%2f1%2f6%2fSubstance_Use_Measure_Advisory_Panel.pdf" title="The Joint Commission Web site">http://www.jointcommission.org/assets/1/6/Substance_Use_Measure_Advisory_Panel.pdf</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180625152856im_/https://www.qualitymeasures.ahrq.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Financial Disclosures/Other Potential Conflicts of Interest</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Expert panel members have made full disclosure of relevant financial and conflict of interest information in accordance with the Conflict of Interest policies, copies of which are available upon written request to The Joint Commission.</p></div></p>
